  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2446",
  "title": "Make the widget showcase use the current version of is.js",
  "body": "Right now, we use the current stable version to generate the [widget showcase](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets.html) on our documentation website. However, for consistency and dev purposes we should use the built version of instantsearch.js (which is generated by docgen).\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the current behavior?**\r\n\r\nIf we try to use, the built version it fails with preact errors and no widget are displayed.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the expected behavior?**\r\n\r\nNo errors and we can see all the widgets.\r\n\r\n**Bug: What browsers are impacted? Which versions?**\r\n\r\nAll\r\n\r\n**Bug: What is the proposed solution?**\r\n\r\nUse the footer_script block to load the scripts after instantsearch.js and make the built version work.",
